  "texts": [
    "However, GMM struggle with modeling complex, nonlinear relationships and dynamic variations in dialect speech signals.",
    "As shown the Fig. 6, there are Chinese DSR traditional approaches' frameworks.",
    "Due to the GMM/HMM hybrid model's fast training speed and the use of probability values to determine the corresponding word level, this approach is suitable for large-scale Chinese dialect vocabulary recognition when compared to Chinese DSR based on DTW.",
    "Despite its high recognition accuracy, the GMM-HMM model has some limitations, including its complex calculation process and difficulty acquiring additional dialect information.",
    "With the development of deep learning technology, an ANN replaced GMM to build the Chinese DSR system."
  ]
